dct_title_s: A description of the coast & city of Goa.
dct_alternative_sm: A description of the coast & city of Goa.
dct_description_sm: Photocopy.   Some relief shown pictorially.   North oriented to the left.   "The city of Goa & all its dependencies doth justly belong to the crown of England by the mariage [sic] of King Charles the Second with Queen Catherine"--upper right.   "21"--upper right.   Outside of original margin is image of British Museum rule and "7-Tab-125." Dimensions: 51 x 61 centimeters
